data.description: ALMOST 5 ACRES of PARADISE in CASTAIC!  Mostly off the grid with Solar, Propane, Septic, private Well, and a small vineyard will power your self-sufficient home in the beautiful hills of Castaic! Looking to build a second home on a lot?  Split the lot?  Acres of room for storage.  The house and the well are connected to SoCal Edison so that the house will not lose power or access to water.  This wonderful 2,297 square foot home with 4 bedrooms, and two bathrooms features an open floorplan with the spacious kitchen which opens up to the dining area.  From there, enter the large backyard 1,100 square foot deck.  Enjoy this wonderful estate on almost 5 acres of land, just over the hill, far away from the noise of the city, but just a 25 minute drive to and from the freeway.  The home also features a laundry room, walk-in pantry, oversized two car garage, custom tile floors and counters in the bathrooms, and much more!  Seller credit available to help you buy down that rate!  Seller is asking significantly less than their 1.2 million dollar appraisal so that they can close on a home they have already found.
